{"tid":179190,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"其實大學係咪令唔少人習慣孤獨","createTime":"2017-03-30T05:35:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-08T17:31:24.000Z","uid":42949,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4bbbd55c94ac090ea60ed8c871b9af33c3efc7d0","tid":179190,"uid":42949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T05:35:17.000Z","msg":"當年中學做乜都係成堆朋友<br />\n上左大學都有班fd既<br />\n但已經開始唔再一堆堆咁玩<br />\n<br />\n好多時候都係自己上堂做野食飯<br />\n朋友都係得閒先約出黎傾下<br />\n<br />\n有好多時一望下 <br />\n發覺其實大學裡面好多人都係自己一個<br />\n就覺得好感觸"},{"pid":"96feeebaad48087db9789bd04264b4d31fc9ffb3","tid":179190,"uid":42949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T05:46:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e5c2ddeace61597d8efc0d348d05662d6300ff0","tid":179190,"uid":11960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T05:47:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcfba52cb20ce47acb5fd6bed74f1f2513656548","tid":179190,"uid":81458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T05:49:10.000Z","msg":"係呀，慣左好多hi bye fd，year one果陣識多，到year four既時候仲會傾計既五隻手指數得晒。岩岩入u唔掛呢種模式，依家成日自己上堂落堂都慣晒冇朋友。"},{"pid":"e96063ebf23efb410cc3c93be242c69986f97492","tid":179190,"uid":81458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T05:49:59.000Z","msg":"係呀，慣左好多hi bye fd，year one果陣識多，到year four既時候仲會傾計既五隻手指數得晒。岩岩入u唔<span style=\"color: red;\">慣</span>呢種模式，依家成日自己上堂落堂都慣晒冇朋友。"},{"pid":"9afc560d3fb6c5e87aed6083414f834eaca92b36","tid":179190,"uid":61106,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T05:51:39.000Z","msg":"睇你有無聯繫架姐，人地唔搵你，你可以搵人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64fc3caef7506d1df67ba1856e76c6adb63fadc3","tid":179190,"uid":81458,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T05:54:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇你有無聯繫架姐，人地唔搵你，你可以搵人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果佢有心做fd既唔洗我揾都會keep到contact"},{"pid":"b6d6d74bbee7546151a912d8f395a69bd543b906","tid":179190,"uid":66203,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T05:56:06.000Z","msg":"正常人每日活動都係自己一個㗎啦 除非約人去街 <br />\n所以係中學特別熱鬧"},{"pid":"be37527a8ff3904569f12acbaf6cf75856efe66b","tid":179190,"uid":42949,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T05:56:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇你有無聯繫架姐，人地唔搵你，你可以搵人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果佢有心做fd既唔洗我揾都會keep到contact</blockquote><br />\n大家都會互約<br />\n不過唔係話成日約囉<br />\n都唔係話完全冇朋友<br />\n不過多數都唔熟 有時寧願自己一個算"},{"pid":"e9b7d8d62b97c4a0d664888fbe0397b3b17df2b4","tid":179190,"uid":42949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T05:58:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係呀，慣左好多hi bye fd，year one果陣識多，到year four既時候仲會傾計既五隻手指數得晒。岩岩入u唔<span style=\"color: red;\">慣</span>呢種模式，依家成日自己上堂落堂都慣晒冇朋友。</blockquote><br />\n我多數識啲朋友就會keep住聯絡<br />\n唔聯絡果啲連hibye都難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a56fbe0c61edeec8c8d23bc5b0833464f0dfdf3","tid":179190,"uid":88382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T05:59:58.000Z","msg":"一定無中同咁好架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c29a26148ff6a9514ee6cd6eb8e55642436ec83c","tid":179190,"uid":15011,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T06:02:46.000Z","msg":"同細o mate好熟<br />\n基本上喺大學成日都同佢地痴埋一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"550901d2beed65638a83569262cb03516eae3b0a","tid":179190,"uid":42949,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T06:06:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同細o mate好熟<br />\n基本上喺大學成日都同佢地痴埋一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm